DEV ENVIRONMENT SETUP INSTRUCTIONS

REPO = the root location of this git repository

1. HOW TO SETUP BASH SHELL

Just add the following line to your current ~/.bash_profile or other variant file:

source $REPO/shell/bash_dev_rc

1. HOW TO SETUP VIM SETTINGS

Just add the following line to your current ~/.vimrc (Linux) or ~/_vimrc (windows):

source $REPO/vim/vimrc

